SELECT COUNT({label/attr.f_owner.salesrep}, {dataset/f_opportunitysnapshot})
  WHERE DATETIME_DIFF({label/dt_oppcreated_timestamp.month}, DATETIME_ADD((
        SELECT MAX({label/dt_closedate_timestamp.day}, {dataset/f_opportunitysnapshot})
          BY {dataset/f_opportunitysnapshot}), -1), HOUR) < 600

SELECT COUNT({label/attr.f_owner.salesrep})
  WHERE DATETIME_DIFF({label/dt_closedate_timestamp.month},
    SELECT MAX({label/dt_oppcreated_timestamp.week})
      BY ALL OTHER
      USING {dataset/f_opportunitysnapshot}, DAY) > 670

      USING {dataset/f_opportunitysnapshot}, MONTH) > 8

SELECT IF DATETIME_ADD(MAX({label/dt_closedate_timestamp.year}, {dataset/f_opportunitysnapshot}), YEAR, 1) = {label/dt_snapshotdate_timestamp.year} THEN 1

attributes.title: Runsum first value of amount with condition

content.maql:
SELECT RUNSUM(FIRST_VALUE(
      SELECT SUM({fact/f_opportunitysnapshot.f_amount})
        BY {label/attr.f_owner.salesrep}
        WHERE {label/attr.f_owner.salesrep} = "Adam Bradley")
    ORDER BY {label/dt_oppcreated_timestamp.year})

attributes.title: Runsum last value of amount with condition

content.maql:
SELECT RUNSUM(LAST_VALUE(
      SELECT SUM({fact/f_opportunitysnapshot.f_amount})
        BY {label/attr.f_owner.salesrep}
        HAVING {label/attr.f_owner.salesrep} = "Adam Bradley")
    ORDER BY {label/dt_oppcreated_timestamp.year})

Sum amount with datetime_add and not between
Sum of amount between max created year and previous year

content.maql:
SELECT SUM({fact/f_opportunitysnapshot.f_amount})
  WHERE {label/dt_closedate_timestamp.year} BETWEEN (
  SELECT MAX({label/dt_oppcreated_timestamp.year})
    USING {label/f_opportunity.id}) AND PREVIOUS(YEAR)

attributes.title: Sum of amount not between max created year and this year

content.maql:
SELECT sum({fact/f_opportunitysnapshot.f_amount})
  WHERE {label/dt_closedate_timestamp.year} NOT BETWEEN (
  SELECT MAX(SELECT {label/dt_oppcreated_timestamp.year}
        BY {dataset/f_opportunitysnapshot})) AND THIS(YEAR)

attributes.title: Sum of amount with case and max

content.maql:
SELECT SUM( {fact/f_opportunitysnapshot.f_amount})
  WHERE {label/dt_closedate_timestamp.year} = CASE
    WHEN {label/county_name} = "Clark" THEN MAX(
      SELECT {label/dt_oppcreated_timestamp.year}
        BY {dataset/f_opportunitysnapshot})
    ELSE "2010"
  END

attributes.title: Sum of amount with if, having and min

content.maql:
SELECT SUM({fact/f_opportunitysnapshot.f_amount})
  HAVING {label/dt_oppcreated_timestamp.year} = IF {label/county_name} = "Clark" THEN (
    SELECT MIN(
        {label/dt_closedate_timestamp.year}, {dataset/f_opportunitysnapshot}))
    ELSE "2009"
  END
